task.summary: NEW README! Added LICENSE, Back to Java 8 again.
Bug fixing, Debian package update Also added CLI desktop launcher

Renewed arch, refactor, bugs fixed, ability to work in a cmdline-only environment as a stand-alone INDI server or as an INDI driver, new control panel, better logs management, changed cmdline arguments, removed some unused code. Still something to fix and to test, serial ports discovery makes its property disappear.
